1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 3=
(Behind the Scenes of a Wealthy Family)

3
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,959
You finally remembered me.

4
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:42,439
My soon-to-be brother-in-law.

5
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:44,920
What are you trying to do?

6
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,920
Qingmei, you married
into a wealthy family.

7
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,840
And now you pretend not to know me?

8
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,159
I am sorry.

9
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,920
I truly

10
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,879
don't remember.

11
00:02:24,719 --> 00:02:26,039
You and I...

12
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,800
It came back to you now.

13
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:31,680
(How did I...)

14
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:46,280
Faking amnesia

15
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,719
is indeed a good choice.

16
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:52,439
You...

17
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:59,159
What is he to me, exactly?

18
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,199
Oh...

19
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,280
Are you waiting for me?

20
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,199
What are you doing?

21
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:12,039
Where's the jewelry from the auction?

22
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,039
Give it to me.

23
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:14,199
I need money urgently.

24
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,599
What do you mean?

25
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,080
Why should I give it to you?

26
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,280
Qingmei,

27
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:25,400
no need to fake amnesia with me.

28
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:28,919
Should I help you refresh your memory?

29
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:34,840
Get lost!

30
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:40,639
Listen up!

31
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,360
Gu Qingmei!

32
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:42,719
What have you done!

33
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:45,800
Having amnesia

34
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:46,960
doesn't make me a pushover.

35
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,039
I...

36
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,800
Did I allow you to come up?

37
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:53,919
Gu Qingmei!

38
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:58,840
Get down.

39
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,120
Get down.

40
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:15,479
Gu Qingmei.

41
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:27,040
Now that you have become the heir,
you think you can just shake me off?

42
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,279
Such a big cash cow.

43
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:31,240
I wouldn't let you go!

44
00:04:36,759 --> 00:04:37,600
You are not asleep yet?

45
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,720
It is still early.

46
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:41,920
Um...

47
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,839
Did you see Jinchuan?

48
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:45,480
I...

49
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:47,319
I am not obligated to
keep track of your husband.

50
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:49,240
Dear.

51
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,519
Why are you in the water wearing that?

52
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:57,399
Swimming, of course.

53
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,199
Why?

54
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,639
Miss me already after a moment apart?

55
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,959
Nonsense.

56
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,639
Your son misses you.

57
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:09,720
You were by the pool, weren't you?

58
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,319
She did not see you?

59
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,519
Maybe I was swimming
underwater just now.

60
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,199
I heard you cannot swim.

61
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,519
Otherwise, I could teach you.

62
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:22,959
Is that so?

63
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:25,240
Are you a good swimmer?

64
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:28,759
Then you must be good at
holding your breath underwater.

65
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,439
That's right.

66
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:33,160
And there might be
some unexpected gains.

67
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:36,920
Are you talking about diving

68
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,319
or swimming?

69
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:40,480
Either way, I am not interested.

70
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,560
And I don't like getting wet.

71
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:49,279
Niannian.

72
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,120
What is wrong?

73
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:54,519
All wet.

74
00:05:54,519 --> 00:05:55,439
However...

75
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:57,800
If Niannian is willing to teach me,

76
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:59,360
I would be happy to learn.

77
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,199
Sure.

78
00:06:00,839 --> 00:06:02,399
If you truly want to learn,

79
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:04,759
we can teach you.

80
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,399
Sure.

81
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:10,279
There might be
unexpected gains after all.

82
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,040
Niannian, let's go.

83
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:13,600
Our little prince must be
getting impatient.

84
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:15,800
Finally, it's come back to you.

85
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:28,519
(Am I really such a player?)

86
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,480
(You're so useless!)

87
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:52,959
(Gu Corporation is selling off shares.)

88
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:54,160
(Just buy them.)

89
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,759
(Yet you failed to acquire them.)

90
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:58,079
(It was indeed my oversight.)

91
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:59,000
(I did not expect)

92
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,680
(that someone else got there first.)

93
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,439
(Someone else got there first?)

94
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:06,040
(There's chaos inside Gu Corporation
right now.)

95
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:08,040
(Someone is behind this.)

96
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,839
(So I am telling you.)

97
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,839
(As Gu Qingmei's husband,)

98
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:14,560
(you should help her more
and care for her more.)

99
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,480
(You hear me?)

100
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,240
Still up?

101
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:23,600
Yeah.

102
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,360
Lately...

103
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,639
How about you sleep here tonight?

104
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:33,439
I will sleep in the guest room.

105
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:40,360
I am just worried that
you are tired from work

106
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,399
and cannot rest well.

107
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,079
No need.

108
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:46,839
I will sleep in the guest room.

109
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,120
Alright.

110
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,160
Goodbye, dear.

111
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:07,800
Dear.

112
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:09,519
Honey.

113
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:12,879
Is An'an asleep?

114
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,959
I just put our little prince to bed,

115
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,519
and now I am here to attend to my queen.

116
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,920
You are definitely
the perfect husband tonight.

117
00:08:22,439 --> 00:08:23,000
Here, dear.

118
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:26,120
I bought this premium bird's nest
for you from overseas.

119
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:27,839
It nourishes the skin and the body.

120
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:30,199
Careful, it is hot.

121
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,440
How is it?

122
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:36,039
Everything you buy is delicious.

123
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,360
But, dear.

124
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:39,960
Don't you think

125
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:42,039
Su Li has changed a lot

126
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,360
since she came back with amnesia?

127
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,600
Is that so?

128
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:47,639
I never really got to know her.

129
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:48,639
Here.

130
00:08:50,159 --> 00:08:51,159
(The current Gu Qingmei)

131
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,919
(is indeed very different.)

132
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:56,320
(Can amnesia change a person that much?)

133
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,879
(News Journalist, Su Su)
This report by Su Su

134
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,600
seems so familiar.

135
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:17,879
You infertile trash!

136
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:20,600
Do you deserve for my son
to spend so much on you?

137
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,000
What a coincidence.

138
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,759
I just read a news report.

139
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:28,480
Saying the latest research shows

140
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,480
that 15% of global infertility cases

141
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:33,120
are caused by defects
in male sperm quality.

142
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,039
What do you think?

143
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:35,639
Why not have your son get checked too?

144
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,080
Shut up!

145
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,480
My son is so outstanding.

146
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:39,759
You are the problem!

147
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,399
You don't deserve my son!

148
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:42,799
I don't deserve him?

149
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:45,519
Your son is not even
worth as much as I am now.

150
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:47,360
You talking nonsense.

151
00:09:51,279 --> 00:09:51,799
Mom,

152
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:54,480
Qingmei is now the
heir of Gu Corporation.

153
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:56,879
You should not speak to her like that.

154
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,559
So this is that supplement
from last year's report.

155
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,519
Even rich people fall for this scam?

156
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,320
Gu Qingmei, where are you going?

157
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:08,679
I can't afford supplements.

158
00:10:08,759 --> 00:10:09,879
I'm going out for some fresh air.

159
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:13,679
Mom.

160
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:22,679
(Relationship Chart)

161
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:23,320
(Relationship Chart)
Boss,

162
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:23,879
(Relationship Chart)
as planned,

163
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:26,200
He Jinchuan's private
renewable energy project

164
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,440
has completely collapsed.

165
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,279
He borrowed a lot of money.

166
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:31,559
Now he wants to borrow more
to cover the losses.

167
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:33,000
Whatever he asks for,

168
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,200
just lend it to him.

169
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,080
Understood.

170
00:10:36,679 --> 00:10:37,200
Boss.

171
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:38,320
We have verified it.

172
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:39,440
The materials on the USB drive

173
00:10:39,559 --> 00:10:41,559
are about Meiyan International's
cosmetic raw materials.

174
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,279
Meiyan International?

175
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:45,440
Does she not know

176
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:48,000
(Meiyan International Raw Materials)
that the one behind is He Jinchen?

177
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,279
(Meiyan International Raw Materials)
I find it strange too.

178
00:10:49,879 --> 00:10:52,360
Those materials seem
deliberately fabricated to smear.

179
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:53,919
Their authenticity has to be confirmed.

180
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:54,799
But over the past few years,

181
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,240
we have been investigating
Meiyan International

182
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:58,399
but no prohibited ingredients found.

183
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,799
Should we continue?

184
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:01,759
Of course.

185
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,320
Eight years ago,

186
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,519
my father was also

187
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,120
one of the shareholders
of Meiyan International.

188
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:10,159
But for some reason,

189
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:12,279
he withdrew his shares.

190
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:13,639
Shortly after,

191
00:11:13,639 --> 00:11:15,759
he died in the fire
at the Meiyan factory.

192
00:11:17,039 --> 00:11:18,559
I don't believe it was an accident.

193
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,720
But He Jinchen is very cautious,

194
00:11:21,399 --> 00:11:23,080
and he operates from behind.

195
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:24,960
It is really hard to get to him.

196
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:27,559
Have you made any progress
with He Jinxi?

197
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:32,799
(I heard Uncle He is looking to
expand into cosmetics.)

198
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,480
(I did not know that.)

199
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,039
(I stay out of company business.)

200
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,360
I've tested her.

201
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,519
She knows nothing about the company.

202
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:44,799
Then should we

203
00:11:45,279 --> 00:11:46,279
start with Gu Qingmei?

204
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:02,399
Boss,

205
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,639
Gu Qingmei...

206
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:05,360
Is she the one who slept with you
and then left?

207
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:09,679
I am just a little curious.

208
00:12:10,879 --> 00:12:12,240
She's not acting at all

209
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,200
like what we had

210
00:12:14,279 --> 00:12:15,080
in our files.

211
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:17,919
Investigate her.

212
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:21,720
Find out why she is looking
into Meiyan International.

213
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:22,559
Yes, sir.

214
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:29,020
(Gu Qingmei)

215
00:12:35,220 --> 00:12:38,700
(He Jinchen)

216
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,320
(I've been followed.)

217
00:13:00,919 --> 00:13:01,639
Who sent you?

218
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,320
What do you want?

219
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:04,799
Give me the USB drive.

220
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:07,360
What USB drive?

221
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:08,960
Are you playing dumb?

222
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:09,879
No, no, wait.

223
00:13:12,519 --> 00:13:14,000
I have quite a few.

224
00:13:14,519 --> 00:13:15,159
Which one do you want?

225
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,879
You're asking for it, aren't you?

226
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,039
Gu Qingmei.

227
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:38,799
Need my help?

228
00:13:55,799 --> 00:13:56,399
Run!

229
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:29,860
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

230
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:34,700
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

231
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:39,260
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

232
00:14:39,260 --> 00:14:44,180
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

233
00:14:44,180 --> 00:14:47,980
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

234
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:52,780
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

235
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:55,700
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

236
00:14:55,700 --> 00:14:58,260
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

237
00:14:58,660 --> 00:15:04,220
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

238
00:15:04,620 --> 00:15:11,420
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

239
00:15:11,700 --> 00:15:16,380
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

240
00:15:16,540 --> 00:15:23,340
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

241
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:30,460
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

242
00:15:30,660 --> 00:15:35,140
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

243
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:38,500
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

244
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:45,420
♪Right as I confess my love♪
